    "ContentDesc_Arkadion - Superschwergewicht R4": "The legendary Lindwurm, a serpentine beast renowned for its unequaled regenerative abilities. The president had long sought to heal his ailing fighters with these powers to no avail, only finding success after making the ultimate sacrifice. But what if the Lindwurm's regeneration truly had no limit─what if it could recover from even the most grievous wound? You imagine that dreadful battle once again, now more dreadful still... ",
    "ContentName_Arcadia": "Arcadia",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_40708_Text": "What power! Looks like someone isn't holding back!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_40711_Text": "Oh dear! The challenger has fallen out of the ring!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_40731_Text": "Another attack evaded with aplomb!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_40732_Text": "Once again they slip beyond their opponent's reach!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_40733_Text": "Oh no, they've been felled with a vengeance!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_40734_Text": "And they're down! Can they recover from this?",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_40735_Text": "They're up! What fighting spirit!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_40736_Text": "And they're back in action! Can they turn the tide!?",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43901_Text": "His arm has a life of its own! Is this the power of the mythical Lindwurm?",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43902_Text": "His arm is slithering out! That's disgusting!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43904_Text": "Watch out! That is one cruel coil...",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43905_Text": "Oh no! The champion's been crushed!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43907_Text": "Dear me, the ring's in pieces!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43908_Text": "Oh no, the gore has latched onto the champion! Don't panic!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43910_Text": "What the─? Could the Lindwurm's regeneration be out of control!?",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43911_Text": "His power continues to run amok! Again and again he remakes his arms!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43913_Text": "Yes, you've got the serpent on the back tail! Press the advantage and finish this!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43916_Text": "The battle is decided! Victory goes to the champion!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43917_Text": "Hm? Is that...the Lindwurm's heart?",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43918_Text": "It's pulsating... I've got a bad feeling about this!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43919_Text": "It's contorting... Transforming!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43920_Text": "Snakes alive! It's the birth of a new Lindwurm!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43921_Text": "Alas, the battle isn't over yet... But don't despair, Champion!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43922_Text": "The Lindwurm is creating more of itself!",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43924_Text": "Some curious props have appeared! What could they possibly be?",
    "Instancecontenttextdata_43925_Text": "Egads, they've taken on the champion's form! This bodes ill!",
    "music_Everything Burns": "Everything Burns",
    "music_The Arcadion": "The Arcadion"
}